query:
UPDATE http_responses SET (
                elapsed,
                elapsed_headers,
                url,
                status,
                status_reason,
                content_length,
                body_path,
                error,
                headers,
                version,
                remote_addr,
                updated_at
            ) = (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP) WHERE id = ?;
